Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:05.60,NEP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354.61,473.31)}Next time: "A New Enemy"
Dialogue: 0,00:22:03.69,00:22:06.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これにて終了ってことで。
